Name: pytest-regtest
Version: 0.0.5
Summary: py.test plugin for regression tests
Home-page: https://sissource.ethz.ch/uweschmitt/pytest-regtest/tree/master
Author: Uwe Schmitt
Author-email: uwe.schmitt@id.ethz.ch
